# Aurora Mission Context

## Platform & Ground System

- **Spacecraft:** Aurora LEO constellation
- **Platform:** OHB (SmartLEO-class, SAVOIR-aligned avionics)
- **Ground System:** GMV HiFly/AutoFly (SPELL-based automation)
- **SRDB:** AUR_V50000.0
- **Orbit:** LEO (< 2000 km)
- **Bus:** Regulated 28 V ± 4 V (24–34 V range)
- **Redundancy:** Cold-redundant OBC (PM-A/PM-B), dual TTC chains, dual CAN bus

## Subsystems & FOP Prefixes

| Tag | Subsystem | FOP Prefix | Scope |
|-----|-----------|------------|-------|
| C-12 | Payload (Comms) | COP/NOP_PLD_ | Channelizer, GPSDO, EPCs, SSPA, PCL, modes |
| C-13 | Payload (OISL) | COP/NOP_PLD_ | Mode ladder, unit power, OISL, DRA |
| CDH | C&DH | COP/NOP_CDH_ | PM, RM, PDIO, CAN, GNSS, CPDU, SW images |
| EPS | Electrical Power | COP/NOP_EPS_ | SADA, battery, BCR, PDU, LCL |
| FDIR | Fault Management | COP_FDIR_ | Safe-mode verify, FDIR on/off |
| GNC | Guidance/Navigation | COP/NOP_GNC_ | Sensors, actuators, attitude modes, calibration |
| PROP | Propulsion | COP/NOP_PROP_ | Hall-effect EP, cathode, PMA, passivation |
| PUS | PUS Services | NOP_PUS_ | Services 1–21 + 128–131, 176 |
| SYS | System | COP/NOP_SYS_ | AOS/LOS, checkouts, FSW, modes, disposal |
| TCS | Thermal | COP/NOP_TCS_ | Heater control, FDIR |
| TTC | TT&C | COP/NOP_TTC_ | Transceivers, RF config, ranging |

