## Aurora Flight Rules

| Rule | Gate | Condition |
|------|------|-----------|
| FR-01 | Conjunction screen | No burn if Pc >= 1e-4 without FD sign-off |
| FR-04 | LOS margin | No critical ops within 15 min of predicted LOS |
| FR-05 | SSPA thermal | TX enable < 55°C, shutdown > 70°C |
| FR-06 | Propulsion valve | Tank T/P in corridor before valve operations |
| FR-08 | Space weather | No GNC calibration if Kp >= 7 |
| FR-11 | Two-operator | Dual concurrence for CRIT-1/CRIT-2 ops |

## Valid PUS Services on Aurora

Standard: 1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 9, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 17, 18, 19, 20, 21
OHB private: 128 (Mode Mgmt), 129 (Device Mgmt), 131 (Reconfiguration), 176

## Spacecraft Modes

SAFE → ACQUISITION → TRANSFER → NOMINAL (and reverse transitions per mode state machine).
SAFE mode: sun-pointing, payload OFF, load shedding active, FDIR autonomous.
